adaptation_attempts:
- Tried switching to fishing from shore but fish populations crashed with changing
  currents
- Attempted to teach traditional knowledge online but felt like preserving artifacts
  of a dead world
- Started buying imported food with government assistance - first time in her life
  not living off the land
- Joined climate activism but felt like shouting at the wind
