vulnerability_details: Like polar bears forced onto land as sea ice disappears, Anyu's
  entire cultural identity and survival skills are built around ice conditions that
  no longer exist. Her knowledge of ice-reading, hunting routes, and seasonal timing
  becomes useless as the Arctic ocean remains unfrozen year-round.
